<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.8.2">
<l>mutalait taṉimā muraṇtī ravaṉṟu mutunīrt taṭattuc ceṅkaṇvē ḻamuyya</l>
<l>vitalait talaicceṉ ṟataṟkē yutavi viṉaitīrt tavammā ṉiṭamviṇ ṇaṇavum</l>
<l>patalaik kapōtat toḷimā ṭaneṟṟip pavaḷak koḻuṅkā lapaiṅkāl puṟavam</l>
<l>matalait talaimeṉ peṭaikū ṭunāṅkūr maṇimā ṭa<supplied>k</supplied>kōyil vaṇaṅkeṉ maṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, worship at Maṇimāṭa Temple in Nānkūr where soft hens</l>
<l rend="indent">unite with [male] doves, [their] green legs like thick coral pillars,</l>
<l>In domed dovecotes on cornices at the front of shining mansions</l>
<l rend="indent">which reach the sky,</l>
<l>The place of the lord who, going to earth that day when he ended</l>
<l rend="indent">the great, unique ferocity of the crocodile</l>
<l>So that the red-eyed elephant in the ancient waters in the pool was saved,</l>
<l rend="indent">helping [it], ended [its] misfortune.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
